headline: Eagle Materials (EXP) Q3 Earnings Lag Estimates
summary: Eagle Materials (EXP) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of -2.92% and +0.36%, respectively, for the quarter ended December 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
